{"tid":389562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"2017日本代表及日本職業聯賽繼續討論 新人入選國家隊只屬陪練","createTime":"2017-09-06T11:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T11:17:16.000Z","uid":33424,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c62665b245a5b04c4916b9d06b5818311f1765ed","tid":389562,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad5589d2c5e3d5f2f0ef02f14ad0b180301e54c","tid":389562,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"網上買飛方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/guide/first\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fguide%2Ffirst&d=eN%2Foexm6BYkdW6HtB%2B3TnzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0a2c3b90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/guide/first</a><br />\n<br />\n第一<br />\nlogin in 無A/C就申請A/C<br />\n申請方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/guide/registration#reg02\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fguide%2Fregistration%23reg02&d=eN%2Foexm6BYkdW6HtB%2B3TnzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b4b4195d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/guide/registration#reg02</a><br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n揀聯賽/球隊/場次<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F01.png&h=9b9c55c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F02.png&h=15135227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n揀位<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F03.jpg&h=a4245aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四<br />\n比錢,領取方法<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F04.jpg&h=aee153be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.信用卡比錢去7仔拎<br />\n2.信用卡去OK同有サンクス、ぴあ便利店拎<br />\n3.信用卡去郵政局拎<br />\n4.去7仔比錢拎<br />\n5.去郵局/銀行比錢之後去OK同有サンクス、ぴあ便利店拎<br />\n6.去郵局/銀行比錢再郵寄<br />\n7.去OK同有サンクス、ぴあ便利店比錢之後拎<br />\n(之後用1,2,7買嘅爸打就去自己所揀嘅便利店襟返個堆數目字就搞掂)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四<br />\n買完<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F05.jpg&h=624b5320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom 日本手足今野秦幸<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HZSwHv_4EAo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHZSwHv_4EAo&d=eN%2Foexm6BYkdW6HtB%2B3TnzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9e2fee58\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HZSwHv_4EAo</a><br />\n樓豬之歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0937bcbb03effef42b42253353517c1037906bc","tid":389562,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"肥雞買飛註冊教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先簡場 有分qr飛同實體飛(小妹要儲飛所以簡實體飛)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qkrjz9wn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqkrjz9wn&h=8655428d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u7nbg8mo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu7nbg8mo&h=530c3bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再簡位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nr709m46\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnr709m46&h=c3155135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sbnydjzx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsbnydjzx&h=aaf50613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數量<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2ry3qi1c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2ry3qi1c&h=f128c848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個位會hold 9分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yam1cl5k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyam1cl5k&h=eb69ea73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再登入(以下為冇ac示範，有ac自己登入)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tnbjvu65\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftnbjvu65&h=7b4e3ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hb2zdcei\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhb2zdcei&h=10d1917c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n填email,密碼<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/f3oh9087\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ff3oh9087&h=8abb46be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡大阪飛腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/emrhpzdc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Femrhpzdc&h=2fd790fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mlf03e26\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmlf03e26&h=c1dafbd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用酒店資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pcwiyxes\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpcwiyxes&h=ddab17e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中国語カタカナ変換<a href=\"http://dokochina.com/katakana.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdokochina.com%2Fkatakana.php&d=eN%2Foexm6BYkdW6HtB%2B3TnzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=02c293ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://dokochina.com/katakana.php</a><br />\n<br />\n我簡信用卡比錢 7-11拎（第一行）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q6ysmucx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq6ysmucx&h=11efaafe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入信用卡資料再禁確定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ksne3qdu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fksne3qdu&h=ff613970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對返資料有冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇就禁確定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/013133_3d1c4543e620e231452dd2788b2b5f9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F013133_3d1c4543e620e231452dd2788b2b5f9b.jpg&h=77abc9da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/up28lgkr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fup28lgkr&h=ad06ee7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qjt24by8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqjt24by8&h=bf65a045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞掂 用個13位code去到7仔拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bumi8dw2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbumi8dw2&h=978f143c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97a7d3579b42214138869d99c8dbc062a0f906f6","tid":389562,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:05:06.000Z","msg":"part2<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到日本之後搵返你簡左拎既地方<br />\n小妹就簡左7-11<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/125924_8ba5e945f9c5c3bcfd53199403a3cabc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F125924_8ba5e945f9c5c3bcfd53199403a3cabc.jpg&h=083ffc2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n排隊搵個靚女姐姐幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/125955_f3466970bf41e63574bb09117d9861ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F125955_f3466970bf41e63574bb09117d9861ae.jpg&h=0b9990e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nShow 13位code 比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個靚女有d老花 放大比佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢打完之後係個moon道禁確定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就會印收據同飛<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/130143_bf925625bb58fc0db95ff31b1aab23a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F130143_bf925625bb58fc0db95ff31b1aab23a2.jpg&h=782283e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢會叫你簽個大名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後包靚靚張飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/130144_0800eac12cb931d9f78425123aa632d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F130144_0800eac12cb931d9f78425123aa632d7.jpg&h=51a8b8a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/130150_bf1c0b945e977b3c965db199273835b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F130150_bf1c0b945e977b3c965db199273835b9.jpg&h=d9fa7628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9776ed30ddee661a8a2d96aaa2371104ba70bd","tid":389562,"uid":95040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80295fc5a6d287e894bdc15906242ab9262cc5ed","tid":389562,"uid":10313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bef25babcd4abf811442e1d5c2009236af264de","tid":389562,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"開過la<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6686ddc83618b5acb2e29981a78b70c2ca8ab5ec","tid":389562,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"打漏左, 此乃po 60<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea060214fa945334a50771507012e9c6b9fe1b5","tid":389562,"uid":10313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開過la<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇冧吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9269397f13b9e45cba9f595dc781a7dcd1d7eac","tid":389562,"uid":95040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地返工/學無wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 點用到咁多<br />\n我每個月都係用3-4gb</blockquote><br />\n樹仁Wi-Fi有=冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=